text: Foscarini is a surname. Notable people with the name include: *Antonio Foscarini (1570–1622), Venetian diplomat *Claudio Foscarini (born 1958) , Italian football coach *Giovanni Paolo Foscarini ( 1600–1647), Italian guitarist, lutenist, theorist and composer *Marco Foscarini (1696–1763), Venetian poet, writer and statesman *Michele Foscarini (1632–1692), Venetian historian *Paolo Antonio Foscarini (1575–1616), Carmelite priest and scientist == See also == *8076 Foscarini, an asteroid
